                            default(Hottel)
                    }
                    ;
                    entry1 = entityType1 == default(IEntityType) ? default(InternalEntityEntry) : queryContext.StartTracking(
                        entityType: entityType1, 
                        entity: instance1, 
                        snapshot: shadowSnapshot1);
                    return instance1;
                } : default(void);
                return instance1;
            };
            return entity;
        },
